name: Tap Tap Fast Pro - Just tap it!!!
name_original: Tap Tap Fast Pro - Just tap it!!!
description:
Tap Tap Fast Pro is a best app to pass your time and improve focus of your mind. Watch out numbers will fall down on screen, tap quickly to destroy them. Game is easy yet challenging. Try to challenge your self to break your own high scores. Once you get high score you can share them on social sites ask friends to break your high score records.

Play now and enjoy the game !!!
